</P>
<P>
University of San Diego finished eighth after the first day of competition at 
the 13-team Cal State Sacramento Invitational at Rancho Murietta golf course. 
</P>
<P>
USD, led by Geoffrey Dean and Rick Schultz, enters today's final round with a 
team score of 623, 30 strokes behind first-place Cal State Stanislaus. 
</P>
<P>
Dean shot rounds of 75 and 74 and Schultz rounds of 78 and 74. USD will compete 
on the South course today. 
</P>
