VALLEY PEOPLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Richard P. Kramer has been named corporate treasurer of Dataproducts Corp., a 
Woodland Hills computer printer maker. 
</P>
<P>
Kramer previously worked as treasurer of PLM International and Transcisco 
Industries, both in San Francisco. 
</P>
